{"tid":1878331,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"53宗！本港今日新增三宗新型肺炎個案　累計53宗","createTime":"2020-02-13T14:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T14:28:39.000Z","uid":9031,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cb2bfc79da27e9ced27226b21cf8a361b075961f","tid":1878331,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:01:47.000Z","msg":"本港再新增兩宗新型冠狀病毒確診個案，連同今日早前公布的另一名確診患者，至今本港累計53宗確診。<br />\n<br />\n晚上確診的另外兩宗確診個案，涉及一名67歲女子及一名37歲男子，兩人為母子關係。他們於上月26日晚上與早前確診的3名患者，即第46、48及49宗個案患者，於北角明星海鮮酒家一同出席聚餐。<br />\n<br />\n確診的67歲女患者，是46宗個案、75歲男患者的小姨，過往健康良好，潛伏期沒有外遊，平日居於鰂魚涌康景花園，周末則居於兒子位於灣仔柯布連道香海大廈寓所。<br />\n<br />\n她於上月31日出現咳嗽，本月1日開始發燒及發冷，分別於上月31日、本月3日及7日向私家醫生求診，昨日到律敦治醫院求醫並入院接受治療。她的呼吸道樣本證實對新型冠狀病毒呈陽性反應，目前情況穩定。她的密切接觸者均沒有出現病徵，將被安排接受檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n37歲男患者過往健康亦良好，居於香海大廈，潛伏期同樣沒有外遊。他於本月8日出現發燒，翌日向私家醫生求診，昨日到律敦治醫院求醫並入院接受治療。他的呼吸道樣本證實對新型冠狀病毒同樣呈陽性反應，目前情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n攬炒加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f942d9bde3e016c5b73c95825c8e6a7bc13b71","tid":1878331,"uid":34764,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"又係一齊食野出事"},{"pid":"d43fc4a0e6f8768ef66fbf041d3049c2904f49b0","tid":1878331,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"未追得上新加坡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61454f5b037f350c31cf0e925cad5e706cd74d6","tid":1878331,"uid":78947,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"海鮮家族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4409ccb03a3f035b8090f09e52ffdc843934709","tid":1878331,"uid":9031,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d43fc4a0e6f8768ef66fbf041d3049c2904f49b0","tid":1878331,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"未追得上新加坡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:04:25.000Z","msg":"知足常樂"},{"pid":"e5322a6df848acd55cc6297e945c6f08f66a5262","tid":1878331,"uid":63287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"go"},{"pid":"f608bed87ec08beffae38600f8fb756317faa66f","tid":1878331,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d61454f5b037f350c31cf0e925cad5e706cd74d6","tid":1878331,"uid":78947,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"海鮮家族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:07:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac3358a9f42e3f17b260d8bc2670e1f0046bf5d","tid":1878331,"uid":155137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d43fc4a0e6f8768ef66fbf041d3049c2904f49b0","tid":1878331,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"未追得上新加坡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:09:46.000Z","msg":"入直路就會透出"},{"pid":"46f55b60416397a5cfd608b104393b6c5587e9f8","tid":1878331,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"二月尾可以儲夠100單??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2273e65bf4affdf6f1197e284fb5422e85941102","tid":1878331,"uid":9031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46f55b60416397a5cfd608b104393b6c5587e9f8","tid":1878331,"uid":166474,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"二月尾可以儲夠100單??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"